at the first thing I learned.

83
00:03:14,224 --> 00:03:15,625
So, start as you mean to go on, that's what I say.

84
00:03:24,053 --> 00:03:29,375
My first game, Rockman, made $7,500 for two weeks of work.

85
00:03:29,375 --> 00:03:30,715
Yay. 1985.

86
